        "subject": "LU-7922 osd-ldiskfs: ROOT inode allocation fix.",
        "message": "LU-7922 osd-ldiskfs: ROOT inode allocation fix.\n\nROOT inode was getting allocated near the end of disk.To\nresolve this problem goal inode is set to guarantee low\ninode allocation for the  directories except precreated\nobjects.\n\nSeagate-bug-id: MRP-2106\nChange-Id: I39de350531aa018a112653937055af5937f14761\nSigned-off-by: Lokesh Nagappa Jaliminche <lokesh.jaliminche@seagate.com>\n"
